snippet.title: Thought-Provoking George Burns Quotes You Should Listen Before Get Too Old!
snippet.description:
Thought-Provoking George Burns Quotes. These are vivid sayings and quotes from George Burns. The best quotes and aphorisms of George Burns that will make you think about many things in life. Quotes from George Burns are definitely worth your time.

George Burns was an American comedian, actor, singer and writer, and one of the few entertainers whose career successfully spanned vaudeville, radio, film and television. His arched eyebrow and cigar-smoke punctuation became familiar trademarks for over three-quarters of a century.

Thank you for watching!
